Text: ESBI Alberta Ltd Merchant Transmission Seminar February advised that the Merchant Transmission Seminar has been rescheduled for Monday February at the Ramada Hotel th Avenue SW Calgary from am pm Please RSVP to Debbie Nering at or by Thursday February The attached link to the ESBI website contains the meeting announcement meeting agenda and ESBIs paper on the Neptune Project Yours sincerely TRANSMISSION ADMINISTRATOR OF ALBERTA Debbie for Fergal McNamara Vice President Startegic Development wwwealabcaabouteventshtml
